# Auto Deploy

- After completing code changes and local verification, deploy the latest version unless the user explicitly says not to deploy.
- For this project, prefer running `npx wrangler deploy` as the final implementation step.
- If deploy fails, report the failure clearly and include the blocking error.
- If the task is read-only, planning-only, or the user only asked a question, do not deploy.
